    "name": "abundant pool pays the covered-loss cap and uses committed boosters",
    "derivation": [
      "eligible = min(100 escrowed, 100 held) = 100 tokens; with 1:1 TWAP and $1 underlying, loss = $100",
      "claim cap = 80% * $100 = $80; the $1000 pool is abundant, so payout = $80",
